@wp.kernel

    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v2
    tmp = wp.exp((tmp - (tmp + 0.34 / tmp + 0.85)))
    v1 = wp.exp(v2)
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.cos(tmp + 0.65) / wp.sin(v0 + 0.29)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.exp(tmp + 1.00)))
